title: "RCM on Import of Services from Foreign Cloud Providers"
description: "Your Indian Pvt Ltd buys Anthropic, OpenAI, or Vercel and the invoice has no GST. That does not mean no GST liability. Here is exactly what the law says."
date: "2026-03-31"
featured: true
